Rjntrnr 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9842] fixed transpose's input/output types
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9828] fixed prepend's type
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9827] fixed the implied collect type to 'any'
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9816] set the rest variable to the correct type
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9802] bumped the version to 0.83
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9836] narrowed the signature of 
``math ceil``
/
``floor``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9830] fixed 
``math min``
/
``max``
 signatures
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9829] fixed signature of 
``split row``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9824] bumped 
``trash``
 in lockfile due to yank
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9794] pinned 
``reedline``
 to 
``0.22.0``
 release
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9793] fixed signatures for cellpath access of records
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9787] updated 
``nu-ansi-term``
, 
``lscolors``
, and 
``reedline``
, and added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9779] Abort type determination for List early
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9778] adjusted signatures for cellpath access of tables
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9777] removed 
``Signature.vectorizes_over_list``
 entirely
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9742] used explicit in/out list types for vectorized commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9741] added explicit input types for vectorized 
``into int``
 form
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9739] fixed output signature of 
``split chars``
/
``words``
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9823] allowed 
``print``
 to take data as input again
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9822] changed the signature of 
``enumerate``
 to 
``any -> table``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9775] added 
``table -> table``
 to 
``into datetime``
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9821] fixed append's signature
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9817] added input_output_type to ansi command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9811] bumped to dev version 0.83.1
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9805] fixed command docs deployment for 
``input listen``
